OL,3,CSumo wrestlers in London preparing
OL,4,Cwith '75kg of rice a day'
OL,6,FAfter more than three decades since
OL,7,Fits first appearance in London, the
OL,8,FGrand Sumo Tournament is returning to
OL,9,Fthe Royal Albert Hall - and the
OL,10,Fpreparations are as mighty as the
OL,11,Fwrestlers themselves.
OL,13,FOrganisers have been busy transforming
OL,14,Fthe iconic London venue into a fully
OL,15,Fauthentic Sumo arena in preparation
OL,16,Ffor the more than 40 of Japan's elite
OL,17,Fmaku-uchi rikishi (wrestlers) set to
OL,18,Fcompete in the tournament, which runs
OL,19,Ffrom October 15-19.
