OL,4,Cwith '75kg of rice a day'
OL,6,FThe arena was built with traditional
OL,7,Fsoil and sand dohyo, and even shipping
OL,8,Fin a roof modelled on a Shinto shrine
OL,9,Fto recreate the sacred setting of the
OL,10,Fsport's spiritual home in Japan.
OL,12,FIn a nod to tradition, audience
OL,13,Fmembers can pay to sit ringside on
OL,14,Fauthentic floor cushions, while the
OL,15,FHall's menu will feature sushi
OL,16,Fplatters and matcha biscuits.
