OL,3,CSumo wrestlers in London preparing
OL,4,Cwith '75kg of rice a day'
OL,6,FBut before the matches begin, the 42
OL,7,Fwrestlers face the challenge of
OL,8,Ffuelling up. They are expected to
OL,9,Fconsume around 75 kilograms of rice a
OL,10,Fday between them during their stay,
OL,11,Faccording to Matthew Todd, the Royal
OL,12,FAlbert Hall's director of programming.
OL,14,FThat works out at approximately 1.7
OL,15,Fkilograms of rice an athlete.
OL,17,FThe preparations for an event of such
OL,18,Fsize go beyond the menu, with
OL,19,Forganisers even installing new
OL,20,Ffurniture to accommodate the rikishi.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/8
