OL,3,CSumo wrestlers in London preparing
OL,4,Cwith '75kg of rice a day'
OL,6,F"We've also had to order in new chairs
OL,7,Fthat can take up to 200kg," Mr Todd
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FThere are no weight classes in
OL,11,Fprofessional sumo, so competitors
OL,12,Foften rely on their size for an
OL,13,Fadvantage, with the average rikishi
OL,14,Fweighing between 100-250kg.
OL,16,FThe event marks the first time since
OL,17,F1991 that Japan's sumo wrestlers have
OL,18,Fcompeted in the UK.
