OL,6,FBack in 1991, hosting the competitors
OL,7,Falso prompted a series of adjustments,
OL,8,Fincluding reinforcing toilets and
OL,9,Finstalling extra-large showers. Local
OL,10,Fhotels also carried out extensive bed
OL,11,Ftesting.
OL,13,FSimilar precautions are believed to be
OL,14,Fin place for this tournament.
OL,16,FThe 1991 basho was watched by sold-out
OL,17,Fcrowds, broadcast live across Britain,
OL,18,Fand introduced millions to the
OL,19,Fcenturies-old sport.
