OL,4,Cwith '75kg of rice a day'
OL,6,FNow, 34 years later, the wrestlers
OL,7,Freturn to London - two of them
OL,8,FYokozuna, the highest rank in sumo -
OL,9,Fto battle it out.
OL,11,FYokozuna Hoshoryu, the 74th of 75
OL,12,FYokozuna in sumo history, told ITV
OL,13,FNews: "I would love for the British
OL,14,Faudience to learn what sumo is and
OL,15,Ffall in love with it.
OL,17,F"Even though it's 15 hours away, I
OL,18,Fhope they visit the sumo arena back in
OL,19,FJapan."
