OL,4,Cwith '75kg of rice a day'
OL,6,FSpeaking about his early years in the
OL,7,Fsport, Hoshoryu said the biggest
OL,8,Fchallenge he had to overcome was
OL,9,Fgrowing his body.
OL,11,F"We eat a lot, and sleep a lot too,"
OL,12,Fhe added.
OL,14,FAhead of the tournament, Hoshoryu and
OL,15,Fhis main competitor, Yokozuna Onosato,
OL,16,Fhave been pictured exploring London
OL,17,Fand meeting fans.
OL,19,FTickets for the event start at #80,
OL,20,Fwith ringside and box packages priced
OL,21,Fover #900 per person.
